query: SELECT r.id, r.coach_id, r.rating, r.comment, r.is_visible, cp.id as coach_profile_id, u.name as coach_name FROM reviews r LEFT JOIN coach_profiles cp ON r.coach_id = cp.id LEFT JOIN users u ON cp.user_id = u.id LIMIT 10
